<span class="token punctuation">}</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><ul>
<li>
<p><code v-pre> baseCompile</code> 方法为真正的编译入口，它主要就是执行了如下几个逻辑：</p>
<ul>
<li>解析模板字符串生成 AST</li>
</ul>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-ext="js"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token keyword">const</span> ast <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token function">parse</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>template<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">trim</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> options<span class="token punctuation">)</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><ul>
<li>优化语法树</li>
</ul>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-ext="js"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token function">optimize</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>ast<span class="token punctuation">,</span> options<span class="token punctuation">)</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><ul>
<li>生成代码</li>
</ul>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-ext="js"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token keyword">const</span> code <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token function">generate</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>ast<span class="token punctuation">,</span> options<span class="token punctuation">)</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div></div></div></li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
