</ul>
</li>
<li>
<p>Virtual DOM 源码中定义：定义在 <a href="https://github.com/vuejs/vue/blob/v2.3.0/src/core/vdom/vnode.js" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">src/core/vdom/vnode.js<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> 中。</p>
</li>
