<li>
<p><code v-pre>_createElement()</code> 方法:  创建 VNode，它定义在  <a href="https://github.com/vuejs/vue/blob/v2.3.0/src/core/vdom/create-elemenet.js" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">src/core/vdom/create-elemenet.js<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> 中:</p>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-ext="js"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token comment">/*创建VNode节点*/</span>
<span class="token keyword">export</span> <span class="token keyword">function</span> <span class="token function">_createElement</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span>
  <span class="token literal-property property">context</span><span class="token operator">:</span> Component<span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token comment">// 表示 VNode 的上下文环境</span>
