<p>path 方法调用 createElem() 方法中的 <code v-pre>createComponent()</code> 的实现:定义在 <a href="https://github.com/vuejs/vue/blob/v2.3.0/src/core/vdom/patch.js" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">src/core/vdom/patch.js<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> 文件中。</p>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-ext="js"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code>  <span class="token comment">/*创建一个组件，创建成功返回true*/</span>
  <span class="token keyword">function</span> <span class="token function">createComponent</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token parameter">vnode<span class="token punctuation">,</span> insertedVnodeQueue<span class="token punctuation">,</span> parentElm<span class="token punctuation">,</span> refElm</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>
