</li>
<li>
<p><code v-pre>arrayMethods</code> 的定义在 <code v-pre>src/core/observer/array.js</code> 中：</p>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-ext="js"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token keyword">import</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span> def <span class="token punctuation">}</span> <span class="token keyword">from</span> <span class="token string">'../util/index'</span>

